{"tid":579482,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［求介紹］架仔朋友突然話黎香港，有咩景點好去？","createTime":"2018-03-03T15:53:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T05:39:18.000Z","uid":64755,"like":57,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"14fd40a9f2d3b25d9842591db63354a1d9379359","tid":579482,"uid":64755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:53:37.000Z","msg":"小弟以前住hostel識左個毒撚架仔，<br />\n佢突然同我講話聽日中午黎香港，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟作為一個毒撚無咩機會招呼外來朋友，<br />\n請問巴打們有無咩景點介紹/好野食推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n預計行程：5小時（佢要轉機去第度，得八個鐘在香港）"},{"pid":"70a58cc0ee367c16421ba5a293441e7289b70f7d","tid":579482,"uid":38904,"like":107,"dislike":2,"score":105,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:54:04.000Z","msg":"信和<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3432432cab9a1f245b1f5b4f8d884425d8629d","tid":579482,"uid":129739,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:55:22.000Z","msg":"帶佢去ifc排apple"},{"pid":"32d20e4e5e12b2ad85bf7af6e01db3866b92c3b2","tid":579482,"uid":21097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:56:08.000Z","msg":"第一次黎hk ?"},{"pid":"f2adde49e668b57e00d88d9f57b69b3357bc1fab","tid":579482,"uid":41394,"like":1,"dislike":54,"score":-53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:56:25.000Z","msg":"中環摩天輪<br />\n黃大仙睇寺廟 / 車公廟<br />\n山頂<br />\n赤柱廣場搵緊對海食個Tea"},{"pid":"9a887888584d84b1ea07f0412c53e348003eb0f8","tid":579482,"uid":169071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T16:00:50.000Z","msg":"酒店囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72d3c8686dde2d556d09bac7647360f2226901b","tid":579482,"uid":125357,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T16:01:07.000Z","msg":"富士大廈"},{"pid":"09d5de906c11d9939efc35bcb0c61db6acbdd0f0","tid":579482,"uid":23194,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T16:02:26.000Z","msg":"帶過美國朋友上山頂"},{"pid":"2e1a5faa1b8cd0c9df6061894493875002dd0256","tid":579482,"uid":64755,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"32d20e4e5e12b2ad85bf7af6e01db3866b92c3b2","tid":579482,"uid":21097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:56:08.000Z","msg":"第一次黎hk ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T16:03:09.000Z","msg":"佢好似短暫停留過幾次,但都無去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea582a7018c70f1b5f2bfefaa707030ac83e2809","tid":579482,"uid":64755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"09d5de906c11d9939efc35bcb0c61db6acbdd0f0","tid":579482,"uid":23194,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T16:02:26.000Z","msg":"帶過美國朋友上山頂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T16:04:02.000Z","msg":"山頂中午/下午有無野好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,<br />\n佢8點鍾機走,我怕佢無得睇夜景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd551771a3be3ba5cb5c4e10a25c80b9cf71e484","tid":579482,"uid":57347,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T16:06:15.000Z","msg":"幾時黎?<br />\n如果3月12日前黎，過開香港島推介ifc2期55樓<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/about-the-hkma/hkma-information-centre/hkma-information-centre.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fabout-the-hkma%2Fhkma-information-centre%2Fhkma-information-centre.shtml&d=%2Fr0XaXq8KzlqI8IwtRVkZ0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=27b2a85b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/about-the-hkma/hkma-information-centre/hkma-information-centre.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n因為睇到香港錢幣歷史之餘，香港個景幾正...<br />\nby the way, 帶㗎仔黎香港咪帶佢食香港地道野囉1"},{"pid":"7fc170497bdd44846f90458526a84cea76034441","tid":579482,"uid":29702,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T16:16:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89ed13c372ff0c24e2a48cfac8afe3e7e11d5e74","tid":579482,"uid":21097,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T16:27:20.000Z","msg":"行下商場食下野算啦<br />\n呢兩日都好大霧"},{"pid":"1d07d3c68b49e3ba43604213788e0b33e280643e","tid":579482,"uid":165404,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"b72d3c8686dde2d556d09bac7647360f2226901b","tid":579482,"uid":125357,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T16:01:07.000Z","msg":"富士大廈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T16:30:58.000Z","msg":"香港都有個富士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f36da1bd12626cf21ed5bdbdaeb5f61618c13e","tid":579482,"uid":61105,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T16:49:15.000Z","msg":"得咁少時間行下尖沙咀，食餐點心，再坐天星去中環坐機鐵番機場算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9eb0ec0a334c3fb92b7dcd46c687fc6563c9d8","tid":579482,"uid":3501,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"38f36da1bd12626cf21ed5bdbdaeb5f61618c13e","tid":579482,"uid":61105,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T16:49:15.000Z","msg":"得咁少時間行下尖沙咀，食餐點心，再坐天星去中環坐機鐵番機場算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:11:29.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n鐘樓 天星小輪<br />\n摩天輪果啲都夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55da07c2e6a8aefadd4f8448580c45ec4dd622ce","tid":579482,"uid":9272,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:13:41.000Z","msg":"1. 機場出中環（機鐵都幾貴 可以的士出東涌再搭地鐵）<br />\n2. 搭山頂纜車上落 係獅子亭影下相落返黎（唔好晒錢去摩天台428） <br />\n3. 可以係中環食下茶記/飲茶 你自己搵；或者山頂落黎搭15c/的士去中環碼頭 再搭天星過TST 先食野<br />\n4. 返機場<br />\n<br />\n1+2 around 個半鐘 至 兩個鐘<br />\n<br />\nHave fun <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3a2c9f92b79c1523584ec7d03f9fb968dc422d","tid":579482,"uid":27251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:15:12.000Z","msg":"富士"},{"pid":"d7c3766b893680565b0879e6d2533a1b5ee03070","tid":579482,"uid":9272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55da07c2e6a8aefadd4f8448580c45ec4dd622ce","tid":579482,"uid":9272,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:13:41.000Z","msg":"1. 機場出中環（機鐵都幾貴 可以的士出東涌再搭地鐵）<br />\n2. 搭山頂纜車上落 係獅子亭影下相落返黎（唔好晒錢去摩天台428） <br />\n3. 可以係中環食下茶記/飲茶 你自己搵；或者山頂落黎搭15c/的士去中環碼頭 再搭天星過TST 先食野<br />\n4. 返機場<br />\n<br />\n1+2 around 個半鐘 至 兩個鐘<br />\n<br />\nHave fun <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:15:33.000Z","msg":"有錢就狂搭的士啦 反正玩得幾個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58b9f6e2d0440a383b0151177fcf7d1509bbc57","tid":579482,"uid":73271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:36:13.000Z","msg":"Kkday 機場快線有特價票賣"},{"pid":"c5eaf63770f1ef71484de8a62a692dcfbe0e9a45","tid":579482,"uid":70808,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:41:34.000Z","msg":"Temple Street<br />\n<br />\nCompare with Japan <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static1.squarespace.com/static/515ce6c8e4b0ba196f61d6d7/t/5444552fe4b0ea3fd72b5032/1413764411400/?format=1500w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic1.squarespace.com%2Fstatic%2F515ce6c8e4b0ba196f61d6d7%2Ft%2F5444552fe4b0ea3fd72b5032%2F1413764411400%2F%3Fformat%3D1500w&h=23ce9a18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e449c72d7f7ee18617b40aa7750f69cef109912f","tid":579482,"uid":132896,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:49:06.000Z","msg":"坐雙層巴士樓上頭位<br />\n<br />\n有次見到啲日本人坐前面好興奮<br />\n<br />\n最好係行大路 又多車 塞塞地 多巴士既<br />\n例如彌敦道"},{"pid":"0f323c5fe2a87cbea38edd1004ce518b54219698","tid":579482,"uid":2172,"like":0,"dislike":60,"score":-60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:55:48.000Z","msg":"其實咁短時間，呢排天氣又咁樣，我建議直接帶佢去香港歷史博物館。<br />\n因為可以幫佢打個底，等佢認識下香港歷史同風俗文化，然後佢往後仲有時間嚟香港留耐啲，再帶佢去啲著名啲嘅景點玩。<br />\n<br />\n但要睇佢本身有無興趣，同埋你要一路為佢講解，最好帶入少少香港真實現景（港中矛盾），所以都要睇返你哋兩個嘅情況。<br />\n<br />\n或者你講下佢對邊方面有興趣？食、玩、買、觀、交流？"},{"pid":"46a09a0cb59d6712914be0611eb287ce29ae8de5","tid":579482,"uid":6275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:56:39.000Z","msg":"女人街"},{"pid":"66541ee0dd82a10e65f51902dd088e3e586dca56","tid":579482,"uid":172494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:56:58.000Z","msg":"香港藥妝 龍城大藥房<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a16fc6304fa68b282d136310cd4019158114418","tid":579482,"uid":6275,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T19:01:50.000Z","msg":"話帶去博物館嘅其實係咪真係帶過外國人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一多數都無乜興趣 第二係咪個個有能力用外語完美解釋香港歷史先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw如果真係要去博物館就去歷史博物館啦 日本人幾鐘意太平清樵同神功戲個到 同埋講主權回歸嗰個戲院仔 入面啲日文報紙做裝飾"},{"pid":"f8250bf1591437e2cc0a66a4ae58c608e47499b2","tid":579482,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T21:27:43.000Z","msg":"廟街新地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f66eb770b2708e8fd34eb190694b13e34d6163","tid":579482,"uid":77134,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T22:38:09.000Z","msg":"食三哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80600829483fa5985557d2edc3f3d845cee38f28","tid":579482,"uid":10637,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T22:42:06.000Z","msg":"架仔咁咸濕梗係帶去玩盡油尖旺"},{"pid":"289496fd34495b1fea5fba4d8b5941b02f5c68ea","tid":579482,"uid":71008,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T22:48:20.000Z","msg":"求其，順便呃d $"},{"pid":"c09a9ee8bc0b5cf61f33ac63c0479f6a3dd6b0d1","tid":579482,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T22:54:20.000Z","msg":"飲茶 去mk行下昅下女掃下街 去茶記食下午茶 完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db03e28b95bb4601b9fcdb00922c0fef6158f846","tid":579482,"uid":156618,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T23:23:14.000Z","msg":"早幾年重讀緊書嗰時有個日本frd (嗰時都係讀緊書)嚟香港玩，我帶佢搭電車 &amp; 天星小輪 , 睇得出佢真係好開心，唔係日本人常見嘅出於禮貌好行嘅「開心」<br />\n<br />\n最衰呢排大霧空氣差，如果唔係可以考慮帶佢坐埋山頂纜車上山頂<br />\n<br />\n至於嘢食方面，我喺佢搭飛機走嘅嗰日嘅朝早同佢去尖沙咀嗰頭搵咗間美心皇宮（好似係）飲早茶，叫啲鳳爪、牛柏葉、鵪鶉蛋燒賣、鴨腳紮之類，感覺上日本茶樓可能冇（我估，其實我唔知日本嘅中式/ 港式茶樓有乜點心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）嘅嚟食，之後佢搭A車巴士去機早，我就去返工<br />\n<br />\nBtw 聽聞日本人好喜歡tempo 紙巾，試下送啲俾佢做手信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a976e5222bab8a157926879c78e5ff987253a81f","tid":579482,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T23:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早幾年重讀緊書嗰時有個日本frd (嗰時都係讀緊書)嚟香港玩，我帶佢搭電車 &amp; 天星小輪 , 睇得出佢真係好開心，唔係日本人常見嘅出於禮貌好行嘅「開心」<br />\n<br />\n最衰呢排大霧空氣差，如果唔係可以考慮帶佢坐埋山頂纜車上山頂<br />\n<br />\n至於嘢食方面，我喺佢搭飛機走嘅嗰日嘅朝早同佢去尖沙咀嗰頭搵咗間美心皇宮（好似係）飲早茶，叫啲鳳爪、牛柏葉、鵪鶉蛋燒賣、鴨腳紮之類，感覺上日本茶樓可能冇（我估，其實我唔知日本嘅中式/ 港式茶樓有乜點心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）嘅嚟食，之後佢搭A車巴士去機<span style=\"color: red;\">場</span>，我就去返工<br />\n<br />\nBtw 聽聞日本人好喜歡tempo 紙巾，試下送啲俾佢做手信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fd0879c327da60e0652fb38861f74e8f1731c327","tid":579482,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score