yle=\"color: red;\">場</span>，我就去返工<br />\n<br />\nBtw 聽聞日本人好喜歡tempo 紙巾，試下送啲俾佢做手信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:52:04.000Z","msg":"係佢地啲紙巾太易爛<br />\n一吹都就穿<br />\ntempo<br />\n京都念慈<br />\n呢兩樣香港其實好出名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:16:37.000Z","msg":"香港特產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋帶佢去食街邊啲小食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01bee71705f0acecaeaf6e11750c6e02bf8f96a","tid":579482,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:22:55.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"1740bf3f719c6c7480c62fc903bd3e33dd3863e9","tid":579482,"uid":144773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:23:55.000Z","msg":"唔係靚囡-&gt;要工作不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e33f5297507ba21cea5d8daabaf7f72f0acc0e3","tid":579482,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:27:01.000Z","msg":"港島就名山，九龍就魚蛋，新界就入元朗<br />\n之前行過粥鋪，見2個架妹指住D油炸鬼話 kawaii<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c3b8dd47a5a2febca9d72e07c3836f2a89738a","tid":579482,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:33:26.000Z","msg":"東薈城 outlet<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得咁少時間去得邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搭得車黎都冇時間玩啦<br />\n最遠最多都係機鐵去到嘅範圍"},{"pid":"409eb0f55bfaaf1e647867138503190972b142a5","tid":579482,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f323c5fe2a87cbea38edd1004ce518b54219698","tid":579482,"uid":2172,"like":0,"dislike":60,"score":-60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:55:48.000Z","msg":"其實咁短時間，呢排天氣又咁樣，我建議直接帶佢去香港歷史博物館。<br />\n因為可以幫佢打個底，等佢認識下香港歷史同風俗文化，然後佢往後仲有時間嚟香港留耐啲，再帶佢去啲著名啲嘅景點玩。<br />\n<br />\n但要睇佢本身有無興趣，同埋你要一路為佢講解，最好帶入少少香港真實現景（港中矛盾），所以都要睇返你哋兩個嘅情況。<br />\n<br />\n或者你講下佢對邊方面有興趣？食、玩、買、觀、交流？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:34:46.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748c670460a9652b4bba41266fbb4543b5d67f9b","tid":579482,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:38:15.000Z","msg":"天星小輪"},{"pid":"5b9ec22e43cc03d6e04afa30d132ad9664937dd7","tid":579482,"uid":371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:53:06.000Z","msg":"帶佢去叫雞算啦"},{"pid":"22a69b0ac559ca220946578e505818cf1af7ec74","tid":579482,"uid":25727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T04:53:32.000Z","msg":"雙層巴士上層最前排"},{"pid":"4a4e9a811df968e906b81d23bfa06123bc3c4656","tid":579482,"uid":45373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"70a58cc0ee367c16421ba5a293441e7289b70f7d","tid":579482,"uid":38904,"like":107,"dislike":2,"score":105,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:54:04.000Z","msg":"信和<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T05:01:45.000Z","msg":"同佢睇下啲老番figure <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3857a90da7e70d9bf8235a06ddbba1e069db743e","tid":579482,"uid":